title: West farmers Carey Mulligan and Marcus Mumford reveal new baby's...
text:
West farmers Carey Mulligan and Marcus Mumford reveal new baby's name By TristanCork | Posted: October 15, 2015 Actress Carey Mulligan on the red carpet for the New York premiere of Suffragette West farmers Carey Mulligan and Marcus Mumford reveal new baby's name X 
Copy link to paste in your message / Comments (0) 
West farming couple Marcus Mumford and Carey Mulligan have revealed the name of their newborn baby â€“ and gone for a traditional one. 
Ms Mulligan, who is currently starring in the movie Suffragette, revealed that their first child was called Evelyn, when asked at the premiere of the film in New York. 
As well as being smallholders on the Somerset-Devon border, Evelyn's father fronts his own rock band that headlined Glastonbury, while her mum is an accomplished actress. 
Unlike other celebrities who take to Twitter within minutes to announce a birth, the couple have kept their private lives scrupulously private. The fact Evelyn had been born was only revealed a couple of weeks after her birth, when Ms Mulligan appeared on the Graham Norton Show last week and wasn't pregnant. Related content
